msgid "gluon-config-mode:welcome"
msgstr ""
"Welcome to the setup wizard of your new Freifunk Westpfalz node. "
"Please fill out the following form and transmit it. <br /> "
"<br /> "
"We recommend pre-appending a regional shorthand (KIB, KL, KUS, PS, ZW, etc.) to the node's name, <br />"
"so it will show up as something similar to KL-Nodename."

